# Case Study Images

This directory contains images for case study examples.

## Required Images:
- saas-transformation.jpg (600x400px)
- crm-automation.jpg (600x400px)
- retail-transformation.jpg (600x400px)

## Image Guidelines:
- Format: JPG or WebP
- Dimensions: 600x400px (3:2 aspect ratio)
- Quality: 85%
- File size: < 200KB per image
- Alt text should be descriptive and meaningful

